# Eval-integrity protected paths.
#
# These files define the evaluation surface of the harness (feature ledger, gate
# thresholds, scorers, judges, validation scripts, the test suite, and CI). Changing
# them can silently weaken what the harness measures, so every change requires review
# by a CODEOWNER. This mirrors scripts/eval_protected_paths.py (the single source of
# truth) and the CI guard in scripts/check_protected_changes.py.

/features.yaml                  @ianshank
/features.schema.json           @ianshank
/scripts/validations/           @ianshank
/config/                        @ianshank
/src/eval_harness/gating/       @ianshank
/src/eval_harness/scorers/      @ianshank
/src/eval_harness/judges/       @ianshank
/tests/                         @ianshank
/.github/                       @ianshank
